Package: xcp-vncterm
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ${dist:Depends}
Description: Provides VNC service for XCP guest VMs
 The Xen Cloud Platform (XCP) is an open source enterprise-ready server
 virtualization and cloud computing platform, delivering the Xen Hypervisor
 with support for a range of guest operating systems.
 .
 This program to expose a virtual machine's serial console as a VNC terminal
 frame buffer.
